and more important

355
00:19:40,710 --> 00:19:41,950
than living.

356
00:19:44,630 --> 00:19:45,290
Since we're

357
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:48,240
both headed to General's Residence,

358
00:19:49,060 --> 00:19:50,060
