360
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:56,350
But...

361
00:19:57,700 --> 00:19:59,110
what you just said about

362
00:19:59,630 --> 00:20:00,950
things scarier

363
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,350
than death

364
00:20:02,910 --> 00:20:03,970
and more important

